#. <section class="sutta" id="sn2.8"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn2.8:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 2"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 2"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn2.8:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamavagga"
msgstr "1. The First Chapter"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn2.8:0.3"
msgid "8. Tāyanasutta"
msgstr "8. With Tāyana"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts1ed" id="pts1ed1.49"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn2.8:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn2.8:1.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho tāyano devaputto purāṇatitthakaro abhikkantāya rattiyā "
"abhikkantavaṇṇo kevalakappaṃ jetavanaṃ obhāsetvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; "
"upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi."
msgstr ""
"Then, late at night, the glorious god Tāyana, formerly a religious founder, "
"lighting up the entire Jeta’s Grove, went up to the Buddha, bowed, stood to "
"one side,"

msgctxt "sn2.8:1.3"
msgid ""
"Ekamantaṃ ṭhito kho tāyano devaputto bhagavato santike imā gāthāyo abhāsi:"
msgstr "and recited these verses in the Buddha’s presence:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn2.8:2.1"
msgid "“Chinda sotaṃ parakkamma,"
msgstr "“Strive and cut the stream!"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.8:2.2"
msgid "kāme panuda brāhmaṇa;"
msgstr "Dispel sensual pleasures, brahmin."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.8:2.3"
msgid "Nappahāya munī kāme,"
msgstr "A sage who doesn’t give up sensual pleasures"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.8:2.4"
msgid "nekattamupapajjati."
msgstr "is not reborn in a unified state."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.112"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn2.8:3.1"
msgid "Kayirā ce kayirāthenaṃ,"
msgstr "If one is to do what should be done,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.8:3.2"
msgid "daḷhamenaṃ parakkame;"
msgstr "one should staunchly strive."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.8:3.3"
msgid "Sithilo hi paribbājo,"
msgstr "For the life gone forth when laxly led"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.8:3.4"
msgid "bhiyyo ākirate rajaṃ."
msgstr "just stirs up dust all the more."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
#. VAR: dukkaṭaṃ → dukkataṃ (bj, pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn2.8:4.1"
msgid "Akataṃ dukkaṭaṃ seyyo,"
msgstr "It’s better to leave a bad deed undone—"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.8:4.2"
msgid "pacchā tapati dukkaṭaṃ;"
msgstr "later you burn for that misdeed."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.8:4.3"
msgid "Katañca sukataṃ seyyo,"
msgstr "It’s better to have done a good deed,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.8:4.4"
msgid "yaṃ katvā nānutappati."
msgstr "after doing which you’re free of regrets."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn2.8:5.1"
msgid "Kuso yathā duggahito,"
msgstr "When kusa grass is wrongly grasped"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.8:5.2"
msgid "hatthamevānukantati;"
msgstr "it only cuts the hand."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.8:5.3"
msgid "Sāmaññaṃ dupparāmaṭṭhaṃ,"
msgstr "So too, the ascetic life, when wrongly taken,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.8:5.4"
msgid "nirayāyūpakaḍḍhati."
msgstr "drags you to hell."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn2.8:6.1"
msgid "Yaṃ kiñci sithilaṃ kammaṃ,"
msgstr "Any lax act,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.8:6.2"
msgid "saṅkiliṭṭhañca yaṃ vataṃ;"
msgstr "any corrupt observance,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.8:6.3"
msgid "Saṅkassaraṃ brahmacariyaṃ,"
msgstr "or suspicious spiritual life,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.8:6.4"
msgid "na taṃ hoti mahapphalan”ti."
msgstr "is not very fruitful.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "sn2.8:7.1"
msgid "Idamavoca tāyano devaputto;"
msgstr "That’s what the god Tāyana said."

msgctxt "sn2.8:7.2"
msgid ""
"idaṃ vatvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā tatthevantaradhāyīti."
msgstr ""
"Then he bowed and respectfully circled the Buddha, keeping him on his right "
"side, before vanishing right there."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.113"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "sn2.8:8.1"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā tassā rattiyā accayena bhikkhū āmantesi:"
msgstr ""
"Then, when the night had passed, the Buddha told the mendicants all that had "
"happened."

msgctxt "sn2.8:8.2"
msgid ""
"“imaṃ, bhikkhave, rattiṃ tāyano nāma devaputto purāṇatitthakaro abhikkantāya "
"rattiyā abhikkantavaṇṇo kevalakappaṃ jetavanaṃ obhāsetvā yenāhaṃ "
"tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā maṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, tonight, the glorious god Tāyana, formerly a religious founder, "
"lighting up the entire Jeta’s Grove, came to me, bowed, stood to one side,"

msgctxt "sn2.8:8.3"
msgid ""
"Ekamantaṃ ṭhito kho, bhikkhave, tāyano devaputto mama santike imā gāthāyo "
"abhāsi:"
msgstr ""
"and recited these verses in my presence.” The Buddha repeated the verses in "
"full, adding:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "sn2.8:9.1"
msgid "‘Chinda sotaṃ parakkamma,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.8:9.2"
msgid "kāme panuda brāhmaṇa;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.8:9.3"
msgid "Nappahāya munī kāme,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.8:9.4"
msgid "nekattamupapajjati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts1ed" id="pts1ed1.50"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "sn2.8:10.1"
msgid "Kayirā ce kayirāthenaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.8:10.2"
msgid "daḷhamenaṃ parakkame;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.8:10.3"
msgid "Sithilo hi paribbājo,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.8:10.4"
msgid "bhiyyo ākirate rajaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "sn2.8:11.1"
msgid "Akataṃ dukkaṭaṃ seyyo,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.8:11.2"
msgid "pacchā tapati dukkaṭaṃ;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.8:11.3"
msgid "Katañca sukataṃ seyyo,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.8:11.4"
msgid "yaṃ katvā nānutappati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "sn2.8:12.1"
msgid "Kuso yathā duggahito,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.8:12.2"
msgid "hatthamevānukantati;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.8:12.3"
msgid "Sāmaññaṃ dupparāmaṭṭhaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.8:12.4"
msgid "nirayāyūpakaḍḍhati."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "sn2.8:13.1"
msgid "Yaṃ kiñci sithilaṃ kammaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.8:13.2"
msgid "saṅkiliṭṭhañca yaṃ vataṃ;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.8:13.3"
msgid "Saṅkassaraṃ brahmacariyaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.8:13.4"
msgid "na taṃ hoti mahapphalan’ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p></blockquote><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.114"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc14"></a>
msgctxt "sn2.8:14.1"
msgid ""
"Idamavoca, bhikkhave, tāyano devaputto, idaṃ vatvā maṃ abhivādetvā "
"padakkhiṇaṃ katvā tatthevantaradhāyi."
msgstr ""
"“That’s what the god Tāyana said. Then he bowed and respectfully circled me, "
"keeping me on his right side, before vanishing right there."

msgctxt "sn2.8:14.2"
msgid "Uggaṇhātha, bhikkhave, tāyanagāthā;"
msgstr "Mendicants, learn the verses of Tāyana!"

msgctxt "sn2.8:14.3"
msgid "pariyāpuṇātha, bhikkhave, tāyanagāthā;"
msgstr "Memorize the verses of Tāyana!"

msgctxt "sn2.8:14.4"
msgid "dhāretha, bhikkhave, tāyanagāthā."
msgstr "Remember the verses of Tāyana!"

msgctxt "sn2.8:14.5"
msgid "Atthasaṃhitā, bhikkhave, tāyanagāthā ādibrahmacariyikā”ti."
msgstr ""
"These verses are beneficial and relate to the fundamentals of the spiritual "
"life.”"
